rgy efficiency. If yours isn\u2019t doing so good, it\u2019s time to look at a modern replacement.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Benefits of a new AC installation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are several significant advantages of upgrading to a new AC unit, including:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Improved energy efficiency<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Long-term cost savings<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Advanced cooling technology<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Avoiding inconvenient breakdowns&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Improved filtration and ventilation features<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smart thermostats compatibility<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Signs you need an AC replacement&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The decision to replace your air conditioner can be a difficult one. That said, there are some sure signs you need an AC replacement, such as:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>An aging unit:&nbsp;<\/strong>Your AC unit is 10-15 years old and showing signs of wear and tear.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Frequent repairs:&nbsp;<\/strong>Frequent breakdowns and rising maintenance costs indicate an aging system.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Poor climate control:&nbsp;<\/strong>Uneven cooling with noticeable hot and cold spots throughout your home.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Inefficient energy use:&nbsp;<\/strong>Higher energy bills due to a decrease in efficiency.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Bad refrigerants:&nbsp;<\/strong>Your system uses the outdated refrigerant (chlorofluorocarbons), which are being phased out.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If your air conditioner is 10-15 years old and still working, yet you have a high energy bill, this is a sign that it is too old for a fix-all repair.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Air Conditioning Installation &amp; Replacement Services<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Medley provides expert residential AC installation and commercial AC installation services throughout Carrollton, TX. We provide different types of AC system installations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Central air conditioning installation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Central air conditioning provides whole-home cooling, sustaining a comfortable temperature throughout your home or office. Our expert technicians install high-efficiency central AC systems tailored to your specific cooling needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ductless mini split installation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ductless mini-split systems offer an energy-efficient cooling solution for homes without ductwork. These systems provide zoned temperature control, allowing you to customize comfort in different areas of your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Heat pump installation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Heat pumps offer both heating and cooling capabilities in a single unit, making them an excellent year-round climate control solution. They are energy-efficient and environmentally friendly, helping to reduce overall energy costs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Zoned HVAC system installation<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A zoned HVAC system allows you to control the temperature in different areas of your home independently. This enhances comfort while maximizing energy efficiency, reducing waste, and lowering utility bills.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Professional AC Replacement Services<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our team provides comprehensive HVAC installation and replacement services, including:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Safe removal and eco-friendly disposal of old AC units.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Installation of high-efficiency air conditioners tailored to your home.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Ductwork inspection and necessary modifications for improved airflow.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smart thermostat integration for enhanced energy savings and convenience.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don\u2019t want to replace your current unit, Medley provides&nbsp;AC repair services. Not sure if you can afford the repairs or replacement you need? We ar